    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just a setback. it's the foundation. if the foundation is rot, the whole building is gone. i look in the mirror and i don't see a person, i just see a decade of wasted time and a lie that everyone finally caught onto. there's no \"moving on\" from this. when your entire identity is tied to being right, being wrong this fundamentally... it just leaves a void. i feel like i'm just haunting my own life at this point.",
